Apple has released iOS 10.2 for its mobile devices. The software update introduces new features, including the TV app (currently US only) and new and redesigned emoji. The TV app allows for a “unified experience for accessing your TV shows and movies across multiple video apps”, said Apple. “This update also includes stability improvements and bug fixes,” said Apple. The new features in iOS 10.2 are detailed below. TV Emoji Photos Messages Music News Mail Accessibility Other improvements and fixes